# Code Insights Summary (Optimized)

## 1. WebMvcConfig.java [Configuration]
Spring MVC配置类，注册UserInfoExtractInterceptor拦截器从Gateway请求头提取用户信息存入ThreadLocal。
- 拦截: `/**`
- 排除: `/error`, `/actuator/**`, `/swagger-ui/**`, `/v3/api-docs/**`

```java
@Configuration
public class WebMvcConfig implements WebMvcConfigurer {
    @Autowired
    private UserInfoExtractInterceptor userInfoExtractInterceptor;

    @Override
    public void addInterceptors(InterceptorRegistry registry) {
        registry.addInterceptor(userInfoExtractInterceptor)
                .addPathPatterns("/**")
                .excludePathPatterns("/error", "/actuator/**", "/swagger-ui/**", "/v3/api-docs/**");
    }
}
```

## 2. HealthReportController.java [Controller]
健康报告HTTP控制器，BFF层处理报告上传/查询，通过Dubbo调用后端服务。

**核心功能:**
- uploadReport: 支持图片(1)/文字(2)/PDF(3)三种类型，文件限制10MB
- queryReportList: 分页查询，支持类型/分类/状态筛选
- getReportDetail: 获取报告详情

**安全设计:** @RequireRole("PATIENT") + @RequirePermission + 资源所有权校验

```java
@RestController
@RequestMapping("/health/report")
public class HealthReportController {
    @DubboReference(version = "1.0.0", check = false)
    private HealthReportAPI healthReportAPI;

    private static final List<String> ALLOWED_IMAGE_TYPES = Arrays.asList("image/png", "image/jpeg", "image/jpg");
    private static final List<String> ALLOWED_PDF_TYPES = Arrays.asList("application/pdf");
    private static final long MAX_FILE_SIZE = 10 * 1024 * 1024;

    @PostMapping("/upload")
    @RequireRole("PATIENT")
    @RequirePermission("health:report:write")
    public Result<UploadReportResponse> uploadReport(...);

    @GetMapping("/list")
    @RequireRole("PATIENT")
    @RequirePermission("health:report:read")
    public Result<QueryReportListResponse> queryReportList(...);

    @GetMapping("/detail")
    @RequireRole("PATIENT")
    @RequirePermission("health:report:read")
    public Result<GetReportDetailResponse> getReportDetail(@RequestParam Long reportId);
}
```

